item.title: About
item.description: About Hi my name is James Kettle. Some things about me that are good to know: I am from NYC, and went to Brooklyn Tech. I lived in France for two years for college. I went to Columbia for Infromation science (kinda a mix of CS and social Science). I really like music, and I make/preform it. I do a lot of programming and looking for work after school. I’m moving to Tblisi for a few months after college but Jan 2024 can relocate where ever.
